.cm SCRIPT REFERENCE APDIXCTL
.cm
.cm   Called with two positional parameters to imbed an appendix.
.cm   The first positional parameter is the appendix letter.
.cm   The second positional parameter is the last update date
.cm   that applies to that source member.
.cm
.ur .if '&UPDATE' ne '' and '&UPDATE' gt '&2';.th .ef
.ur .tt /SCRIPT//APPENDIX &1/
.ur .if '&SCENTRE' = 'YES' .th .ur .et /APPENDIX &1//SCRIPT/
.ur .sr apndix&1=%
.sa
.ur .im APENDIX&1
.pa
.re
.cm End of APDIXCTL
